The NEWS file for the lwnetrouter package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v2.0.0rc0 - 25 June 2025

The first v2.x release candidate.

Changes:
  Qt Toolkit. Upgraded the required Qt dependency to Qt6.

  Delay Control. Modified the 'lwnetrouter' service to use the standard
  'cunctator' control protocol, allowing the cunc(1) GUI applet to be used
  for delay control. Removed the lwnetdelay(1) GUI applet.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.1 - 27 February 2018

Bugfixes. See the ChangeLog for details.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v1.0.0 - 21 February 2018

The first production release.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
